query.sfwSql: Select a.*,b.org_id from sgt_wss_member_record_request a inner join SGT_WSS_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT b on a.MEMBER_RECORD_REQUEST_ID=b.MEMBER_RECORD_REQUEST_ID where (status_value='REVW' or status_value='RJTD')
Select a.*,b.org_id from sgt_wss_member_record_request a inner join SGT_WSS_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT b on a.MEMBER_RECORD_REQUEST_ID=b.MEMBER_RECORD_REQUEST_ID

SELECT P.*, B.*,B.ORG_ID, ISNULL((SELECT TOP 1 REQ.EMPLOYMENT_CHANGE_REQUEST_ID FROM SGT_WSS_EMPLOYMENT_CHANGE_REQUEST REQ WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE REQ.PERSON_ID = P.PERSON_ID AND REQ.ORG_ID = B.ORG_ID AND REQ.STATUS_VALUE IN ('REVW', 'RJTD') AND REQ.CHANGE_TYPE_VALUE = 'TEEM'), 0) AS iintTermEmpID FROM SGT_PERSON P WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT B WITH(NOLOCK) ON B.PERSON_ID = P.PERSON_ID AND( B.END_DATE IS NULL OR B.END_DATE>GETDATE()) ORDER BY P.LAST_NAME, P.FIRST_NAME
select * from sgt_organization c WITH(NOLOCK) where c.org_id = b.org_id

Select a.*,b.org_id, a.MODIFIED_BY AS istrRejectedByName from sgt_wss_member_record_request a inner join SGT_WSS_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT b on a.MEMBER_RECORD_REQUEST_ID=b.MEMBER_RECORD_REQUEST_ID where (status_value='REVW' or status_value='RJTD') and b.org_id = @ORGID AND DATEDIFF(d,a.MODIFIED_DATE,GETDATE()) <=90

SELECT * FROM SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DETAIL DET INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_EMPLOYMENT_DETAIL PA ON PA.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID=DET.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID AND PA.ELECTION_VALUE = 'ENLD' INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA ON PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID=SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE DET.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID=B.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID

SELECT SCI.* FROM SGW_BPM_CASE_INSTANCE SCI WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGW_BPM_REQUEST BR WITH(NOLOCK) ON SCI.REQUEST_ID = BR.REQUEST_ID AND BR.REQUEST_ID = @REQUEST_ID INNER JOIN SGW_BPM_PROCESS_INSTANCE SPI WITH(NOLOCK) ON SCI.CASE_INSTANCE_ID = SPI.CASE_INSTANCE_ID INNER JOIN SGW_BPM_PROCESS SP WITH(NOLOCK) ON SP.PROCESS_ID = SPI.PROCESS_ID INNER JOIN SGW_BPM_PROCESS_ID_DESC SPD WITH(NOLOCK) ON SP.DESCRIPTION = SPD.DESCRIPTION AND SP.PROCESS_ID = @PROCESS_ID
SELECT * FROM SGT_WSS_MEMBER_RECORD_REQUEST WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE STATUS_VALUE = 'PEND' AND ISNULL(BPM_INITIATED, 'N') = 'N'
